3) Organization of the folders and their dependancies
----------------------------------------------------

     The 3 folders have the following structures

     - pmip6d/	 	contains all the files for the PMIP6D tool

     - /etc/match	is a text file, used like a database which contains the link between a MN's MAC Address and its PMIP network prefix 

      PMIP6D is quite independent from the other OpenAirInterface blocks.
    
