5)  How to run a simple experimentation
----------------------------------------------------------------

      In order to create a PMIP domain composed of 3 nodes (1 LMA + 2 MAGS) :
	
	They all three are in the network which has for IPv6 prefix 2001:100::/64
	With LMA: nasmesh0=2001:100::1  /  MAG1: nasmesh0=2001:100::2 & eth0=2001:1::2  /  MAG2: nasmesh0=2001:100::3 & eth0=2001:1::3

	On LMA execute ->  pmip6d -c -i -L 2001:100::1
	On MAG1 execute -> pmip6d -m -i -L 2001:100::1 -N 2001:1::3 -E 2001:100::2
	On MAG2 execute -> pmip6d -m -i -L 2001:100::1 -N 2001:1::2 -E 2001:100::3

